// ============================================================================
// AGGRESSIVE CONFIG EXAMPLE
// ============================================================================
//
// All five strategies enabled with larger position sizes and looser filters.
// Designed for users who have already run the Conservative or Balanced profile
// in live trading and want to push harder.
//
// ⚠️  This is a STARTING POINT for an aggressive profile, not a proven formula.
//     Every market is different. Monitor closely and tune from here.
//
// Good for: experienced users, wallets of $200+, high-volatility sessions.
//
// To use: copy this file to src/config.rs, then `cargo build --release`.
// ============================================================================

use rust_decimal::Decimal;
use rust_decimal_macros::dec;
use std::time::Duration as StdDuration;

